Package ch.nolix.core.endPoint

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IEndPointTaker
    An end point taker can take end points.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EndPoint
    An end point can send messages to an other end point of the same type.
    LocalEndPoint
    A local end point can send messages to an other local end point which is its counterpart.
    NetEndPoint
    A net end point is an end point that can send messages to an other net end point that is: -on the same process on the local machine -on an other process on the local machine -on an other machine
    NetServer
    A net server is a server that listens to net end points on a specific port.
    Server
    A server manages an end point taker.
